headline: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. Acquires Shepard Insurance Group
summary: Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. today announced the acquisition of Old Greenwich, Connecticut-based Shepard Insurance Group. Terms of the transaction were not disclosed.
